com.camerontec.catalys.core.marketstate

Class OrderArchiveLog

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.camerontec.catalys.core.marketstate.OrderArchiveLog
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    IOrderArchive

    public class OrderArchiveLog
extends Object
implements IOrderArchive
    Default implementation of IOrderArchive based on IArchiveLog.

    It keeps an in-memory map (size and position) of order records archived to a file.

      • getFillEntry

        public ITagValues getFillEntry(String clOrdID,
                               int tag,
                               String value)
        Description copied from interface: IOrderArchive
        Retrieves the fill for order with the given tag/value from archive. Note that this will return the original values of this fill, ignoring any later corrections or cancellations of this fill.

        If more than one exists, any one could be returned.

        Specified by:
        getFillEntry in interface IOrderArchive
        Parameters:
